flowchart LR
    A[Input: User Preferences] --> B[Load songs from CSV]
    B --> C[Pick next song row]
    C --> D[Genre match? Add +2.0 if yes]
    D --> E[Mood match? Add +1.0 if yes]
    E --> F[Compute energy similarity points 0.0 to 1.0]
    F --> G[Total score for this song]
    G --> H[Store song and score]
    H --> I{More songs left?}
    I -->|Yes| C
    I -->|No| J[Sort all songs by score descending]
    J --> K[Select Top K]
    K --> L[Output: Ranked recommendations]
